\f0\fs24 \cf0 \cb1 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 In this method, coseismic slip is computed assuming uniform stress drop on a fault plane with unknown geometry and unknown area of the fault plate that is allowed to slip. \
